description: Nestled on a quiet dead-end street, this rare 3-bedroom, 2-bath condo offers the perfect blend of tranquility and vibrant city living. Step through your private townhouse-style entrance into a sun-filled, open floor plan designed for effortless living and entertaining. The kitchen boasts granite countertops and a stylish peninsula—ideal for hosting. The true showstopper? Your private, deeded yard with a deck, shed, and garden—perfect for summer BBQs, morning coffee, or unwinding in your outdoor retreat. The main level offers two bedrooms, while the lower level is a private sanctuary featuring a primary suite with a gas fireplace, slate shower, office space, closets, and laundry. Just minutes from bus lines, beaches, and Southie’s top dining spots! Don't miss this opportunity see it anytime!
